HELM: package manage for kubernetes.
To deploy multiple YAML files with one command.

Helm charts: chart --> application manager.
Package format used to define, install, manage applications in kubernetes.
We can deploy applications using multiple YAML files.

Types of  Helm  charts:
	1. Application: deploy application, default helm chart.
	2. Library: store, reuse the helm templates in multiple application charts.


